ZH: 他说实话就好，不要出尔反尔。
EN: Just tell the truth, don’t be wishy-washy.

ZH: 她总是出尔反尔，让人很难相信她。
EN: She’s always saying one thing and doing another, making it hard to trust her.

ZH: 我不喜欢和出尔反尔的人交朋友。
EN: I don’t like being friends with people who are wishy-washy.

ZH: 他出尔反尔的态度让公司的合作伙伴很难相处。
EN: His wishy-washy attitude makes it difficult for the company’s partners to deal with him.

ZH: 别再出尔反尔了，时间都浪费在你身上了！
EN: Stop being wishy-washy, we’re wasting time on you!

