EN: No one likes dealing with wishy-washy people.

ZH: 她总是出尔反尔，让人难以理解。
EN: She’s always changing her mind, making it hard to understand her.

ZH: 出尔反尔的态度让整个团队都很难一起工作。
EN: Wishy-washy attitudes make it difficult for the whole team to work together.

